lead_paragraph: British and Irish Lions coach Warren Gatland has said he felt "embarrassed" to be a New Zealander after sitting amid a parochial crowd during an All Blacks match at Auckland's Eden Park.

headline.print_headline: Jeering Crowd Made Gatland 'Embarrassed' to Be New Zealander
